==Playing style==
Saed Al-Rosan is able to play as a [[Defender (association football)|center-back]] and as a [[Midfielder (association football)|defensive-midfielder]], having the ability to create plays.<ref>{{cite web |title=الحسين إربد يتعاقد مع الروسان |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1003861&pg=1&o=n3132788 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |language=Arabic |date=17 February 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=الحسين إربد يجدد عقد الروسان |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1103142&pg=1&o=n3132788 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |language=Arabic |date=12 January 2022}}</ref>

